## Overview

Basketball-IQ is a React Native Android application that applies a **multi-variable Bayesian regression algorithm** (validated at 70.6% win rate against DraftKings closing lines, 2015–2026) to generate NBA point guard prop-bet recommendations.

Focus areas:
- PG Assists Over/Under
- PG Turnovers Over/Under
- Team Total Assists Over/Under
- PG vs PG head-to-head matchup covariance
- Coach defensive system encoding

