## Installation

### Prerequisites
- Node.js 18+
- React Native CLI
- Android Studio with Android SDK
- Java 17 (for Android builds)

### Setup
```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/Basketball-iq.git
cd Basketball-iq
npm install

# Android
npx react-native run-android
```

### API Keys (optional — app works with mock data without keys)
Create a `.env` file in the root:
```env
# The Odds API (free: 500 req/month) — https://the-odds-api.com
ODDS_API_KEY=your_key_here

# Optional: OpenAI for AI narrative generation
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_key_here
```

### Run Backtest
```bash
npx ts-node src/algorithm/BacktestRunner.ts
```

