## API Integrations

### DraftKings
- **Method:** The Odds API wrapper (DraftKings doesn't have a public API)
- **Data:** Game lines, spreads, totals, player props (assists, turnovers, PRA)
- **Update frequency:** Every 5 minutes when markets are open

### Sleeper
- **Official public API** — no key required
- `GET /v1/players/nba` — all player metadata including injury status
- `GET /v1/players/nba/trending/drop` — real-time injury detection signal
- `GET /v1/stats/nba/{season}/{week}` — weekly player stats

### NBA Stats (stats.nba.com)
- **Public but header-restricted** — requires proper User-Agent / Origin headers
- `playergamelog` — last N game stats per player
- `leaguedashptteamdefend` — defense vs. position data
- `leaguedashteamstats` — team advanced metrics (pace, AST%, OffRtg)

